<section class="section section--sides section--graphic-right">
    <span class="anchor-target" id="feature-rich-reseller-hosting"></span>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section__title">
            Feature-Rich Reseller Hosting
        </h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-xl-6 col-lg-7 ">
                <div class="section__content">
                    <h3 class="section__title h4">
                        Your business, our products
                    </h3>
                    <p class="section__desc">
                        Reseller hosting allows you to earn money by becoming your very own web hosting company.
                        You’ll be in control of all aspects of your business and we’ll stay behind the curtain.
                        You’ll reap all the benefits and we’ll do all the work. You can thank us later!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
